txt.en: Gropor, you are here to assist with a raid on Ost Guruth. Make your way north into the village and terrorize players. You have three hours to complete this task. If you are slain, your session will end.
Join the raid on Ost Guruth!
Fight the people of Ost Guruth, you have three hours of time to spare.
You will be logged to your admin when you die.
